msgstr "If checked, use 2*m/n of limited-time stamina potions (rounded up)."

msgid ""
"子任务开关用⭐标出，自上而下顺序执行，最后执行『日常奖励』。\n"
"如果出现反复按ESC的情形，请调高『设置/主界面单次动作后延迟』（建议1.5以上）。"
msgstr ""
"Sub-tasks marked with ⭐, top to bottom, Daily Rewards last.\n"
"If ESC repeats, increase Action Delay (recommended 1.5+)."

