msgstr ""
"Visit friend's Dijiang, assist at Visitor Terminal, then collect at Credit "
"Exchange."

msgid "是否前往好友的「帝江号」并在「访客终端」上进行收集线索、制造舱操作"
msgstr "Visit friend's Dijiang for clue collection and manufacturing"

